{"tid":852462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳中共想向特朗普講和, 借建交40周年邀請訪華","createTime":"2018-10-08T01:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T23:34:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":134,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"3b494bba4405ce7bf1771e91c7baac627f074440","tid":852462,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:04:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181007/58768324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181007%2F58768324&d=VZw3MJ3HFo%2B70rSU20z6mjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=951e347e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181007%2F58768324&h=af39fdba\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181007/58768324</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月07日 <br />\n【中美有彎轉？】傳北京想講和 借建交40周年邀請侵侵訪華<br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯日前發表對華極其強硬的講話，令正處貿易戰中的中美兩國，關係更形惡化，甚至被外界視為中美「新冷戰」已經開始。不過，今日突然傳出，中國想利用明年中美建交40周年這個契機，與美國講和。<br />\n<br />\n據多名內地官員及智囊透露，中南海領導層希望於2019年1月1日，隆重紀念中美建交40周年，並希望於今年年底紀念中美聯合聲明發表40周年。中央希望借此邀請美國總統特朗普再度訪華，修補目前的裂痕。目前，中央多名智囊正籌備中。<br />\n<br />\n微信"},{"pid":"51eeed33927b044c5b878aeacdb060d53516ee6a","tid":852462,"uid":10890,"like":392,"dislike":2,"score":390,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/08/090634_0cb9650420f1cd2c8aaf48fc79423922.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F08%2F090634_0cb9650420f1cd2c8aaf48fc79423922.png&h=2350cb3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2061fd3c75b2d19301be000037fbd15badbb4f83","tid":852462,"uid":82033,"like":259,"dislike":0,"score":259,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:08:29.000Z","msg":"主客都唔識分？主動訪美啦"},{"pid":"cf721f8447ae86d254751d3a9290c56f2f510e8f","tid":852462,"uid":70238,"like":158,"dislike":1,"score":157,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T0